content.description: I'm guessing this project is in the V12 realm. Start in the Flatanger Cave, and head up and left through the obvious roof. I have no idea if this goes.
content.location: Flatanger Boulder has a cave at the bottom of it, named after the giant cave in Flatanger, Norway. Of course, this might be just a little smaller. Flatanger Boulder is accessed by going to Moai Boulder. If you're looking at Moai, turn 90 degrees right and walk 1 minute. You'll know you're there because there's a small cave on the southeast corner.

content.description: Flatanger sit starts in the cave on the southeast corner and heads up the finger crack. It is a super fun line.
